arcade.agent.helper

Class MoveTissueHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • arcade.agent.helper.TissueHelper
      • arcade.agent.helper.MoveTissueHelper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Helper, java.io.Serializable, sim.engine.Steppable

    public class MoveTissueHelper
extends TissueHelper
    Extension of TissueHelper for cell movement.

    MoveTissueHelper is stepped once after the number of ticks corresponding to (distance to move)*(movement speed) has passed. The MoveTissueHelper will move the cell from one location to another based on best location as determined by the getBestLocation method in TissueCell.

    Since:
    2.2
    Version:
    2.3.6
